title: Honolulu museum returning totem pole to Alaska
text:
Honolulu museum returning totem pole to Alaska Published 1:54 PM HST Oct 22, 2015 A Large Text Photos 
A Hollywood icon, a legendary horror actor, and a totem pole all combine for a "you can't make this up" story at the Honolulu Museum of Art. Related 
Tonight, see how a totem pole once stolen by John Barrymore and later purchased by Vincent Price wound up at the Honolulu Museum of Art. 
And see the ceremony held before the pole was returned to Alaska. 
Paula Akana has the story, only on KITV News at 6.
